Class LazyValueMap

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,Value>

    public final class LazyValueMap
extends ForwardingMap<String,Value>
    An immutable dictionary of response nodes. FaunaDB responses can be polymorphic, so this dictionary allows individual entries to be coerced to concrete response types as required.
    See Also:
